<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="8Apr1928"><font color="red">8 April 1928</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Harriet Weaver): Svevo has sent me Veruda&apos;s portrait of his redheaded wife, Mrs S. (v. Anna Livia: her name is Livia S.) &hellip; The transition people are beginning to bother me again for the June instalment but I have not energy enough to say yes, aye or no </div>
